#: ../../../prop_sf/LABELS.rst:2
msgid "LABELS"
msgstr "LABELS"

#: ../../../prop_sf/LABELS.rst:4
msgid "Specify a list of text labels associated with a source file."
msgstr "指定與來源檔相關聯的一串文字標籤。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/LABELS.rst:6
msgid ""
"This property has meaning only when the source file is listed in a target "
"whose :prop_tgt:`LABELS` property is also set.  No other semantics are "
"currently specified."
msgstr ""
"此屬性僅當來源檔案被列在一個也設定了 :prop_tgt:`LABELS` 屬性的目標中時才有意"
"義。目前未指定其他語意。"
